message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and question answering. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) in decreasing order of likelihood.
